{"title":"Mac(M1)常用环境安装","uid":"68fffcca682c31267962b9be63cae57a","slug":"mac","date":"2021-06-06T00:55:28.000Z","updated":"2021-06-06T08:00:59.538Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/mac.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://www.apple.com.cn/v/macbook-pro-13/g/images/overview/hero_endframe__bsza6x4fldiq_large_2x.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"1-引言\"><a href=\"#1-引言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.引言\"></a>1.引言</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>最近更换了Macbook Pro M1版，这也是第一次接触Mac，才一天时间就彻底征服我了。整理一下后端开发中常用的一些环境的安装</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"2-环境安装\"><a href=\"#2-环境安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.环境安装\"></a>2.环境安装</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>话不多说，开搞</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-1-jdk安装\"><a href=\"#2-1-jdk安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 jdk安装\"></a>2.1 jdk安装</h2><ul>\n<li>目前jdk有适配arm架构的zulu版本，直接下载安装即可</li>\n<li>下载地址：<a href=\"https://www.azul.com/downloads/?package=jdk\">https://www.azul.com/downloads/?package=jdk</a></li>\n<li>选择对应版本下载直接安装</li>\n<li>环境变量会自动配置，安装完成后在命令行检验即可</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">markcwg@192 ~ % java -version\nopenjdk version &quot;1.8.0_292&quot;\nOpenJDK Runtime Environment (Zulu 8.54.0.21-CA-macos-aarch64) (build 1.8.0_292-b10)\nOpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (Zulu 8.54.0.21-CA-macos-aarch64) (build 25.292-b10, mixed mode)</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-2-maven安装\"><a href=\"#2-2-maven安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 maven安装\"></a>2.2 maven安装</h2><ul>\n<li><p>maven也是直接从官网安装即可</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>下载地址： <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi\">http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>下载对应的tar.gz包，解压到自己的目录(我的是 /Users/markcwg/dev/apache-maven-3.8.1/)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置环境变量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">vim ~&#x2F;.bash_profile\n\n#以下是配置内容,MAVEN_HOME之后的内容换成自己的安装地址\nexport MAVEN_HOME&#x3D;&#x2F;Users&#x2F;markcwg&#x2F;dev&#x2F;apache-maven-3.8.1\nexport PATH&#x3D;$PATH:$MAVEN_HOME&#x2F;bin</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>由于重启后默认使用的是 <code>~/.zshrc</code>配置文件，所以还需要编辑一下 <code>~/.zshrc</code>文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo vim ~&#x2F;.zshrc\n#在这里刷新bash_profile即可\nsource ~&#x2F;.bash_profile</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>配置完成后刷新配置文件 <code>source ~/.zshrc</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>检查是否安装成功</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">markcwg@192 ~ % mvn -v\nApache Maven 3.8.1 (05c21c65bdfed0f71a2f2ada8b84da59348c4c5d)\nMaven home: &#x2F;Users&#x2F;markcwg&#x2F;dev&#x2F;apache-maven-3.8.1\nJava version: 1.8.0_292, vendor: Azul Systems, Inc., runtime: &#x2F;Library&#x2F;Java&#x2F;JavaVirtualMachines&#x2F;zulu-8.jdk&#x2F;Contents&#x2F;Home&#x2F;jre\nDefault locale: zh_CN, platform encoding: UTF-8\nOS name: &quot;mac os x&quot;, version: &quot;11.4&quot;, arch: &quot;aarch64&quot;, family: &quot;mac&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-3-homebrew安装\"><a href=\"#2-3-homebrew安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3 homebrew安装\"></a>2.3 homebrew安装</h2><ul>\n<li><p>mac上很多东西都通过brew安装</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装homebrew的过程并不是很友好，试了很多方法</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>最后在一位大佬的博客里成功找到解决方案</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一行代码直接搞定</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;zsh -c “$(curl -fsSL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitee.com&#x2F;feraljas&#x2F;HomebrewCN&#x2F;raw&#x2F;master&#x2F;Homebrew.sh)”</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>运行脚本之后直接在线安装，脚本运行过程中的关键步骤提示是中文，跟着走完就完事了</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-4-svn和git安装\"><a href=\"#2-4-svn和git安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.4 svn和git安装\"></a>2.4 svn和git安装</h2><ul>\n<li>作为常用的版本控制工具，开发过程中肯定是少不了的</li>\n<li>这两个的安装都不算难，直接利用homebrew命令行安装就好了</li>\n<li><code>brew install svn</code></li>\n<li><code>brew install git</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-5-idea安装\"><a href=\"#2-5-idea安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.5 idea安装\"></a>2.5 idea安装</h2><ul>\n<li>作为java后端开发程序员，idea是少不了的(嘿嘿，反正对我来说是少不了的)</li>\n<li>目前 jetbrains 已经有适配版的安装包，按需下载即可</li>\n<li>下载地址： <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/idea/download/#section=mac\">https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/idea/download/#section=mac</a></li>\n<li>注意下载的时候选择 Apple Silicon芯片版</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-6-postman安装\"><a href=\"#2-6-postman安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.6 postman安装\"></a>2.6 postman安装</h2><ul>\n<li>postman用于接口测试</li>\n<li>下载地址：<a href=\"https://www.postman.com/downloads/\">https://www.postman.com/downloads/</a></li>\n<li>直接下载安装即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-7-vscode安装\"><a href=\"#2-7-vscode安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.7 vscode安装\"></a>2.7 vscode安装</h2><ul>\n<li>vscode的安装也很简单</li>\n<li>下载地址： <a href=\"https://vscode.cdn.azure.cn/insider/861a88ebadb4335df92251faf6420b598440e082/VSCode-darwin-arm64.zip\">https://vscode.cdn.azure.cn/insider/861a88ebadb4335df92251faf6420b598440e082/VSCode-darwin-arm64.zip</a></li>\n<li>打开这个链接会直接开始下载，正常安装即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-8-nodejs安装\"><a href=\"#2-8-nodejs安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.8 nodejs安装\"></a>2.8 nodejs安装</h2><ul>\n<li>node的安装也是直接在官网即可</li>\n<li>下载地址： <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a></li>\n<li>安装完成后验证</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">markcwg@192 ~ % node -v\nv14.17.0\nmarkcwg@192 ~ % npm -v\n6.14.13</code></pre>\n\n","feature":false,"text":"1.引言 最近更换了Macbook Pro M1版，这也是第一次接触Mac，才一天时间就彻底征服我了。整理一下后端开发中常用的一些环境的安装 2.环境安装 话不多说，开搞 2.1 jdk安装 目前jdk有适配arm架构的zulu版本，直接下载安装即可 下载地址：https://w...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"知识分享","slug":"知识分享","count":1,"path":"api/categories/知识分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"后端开发","slug":"后端开发","count":3,"path":"api/tags/后端开发.json"},{"name":"Mac","slug":"Mac","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Mac.json"},{"name":"换机","slug":"换机","count":1,"path":"api/tags/换机.json"},{"name":"环境安装","slug":"环境安装","count":1,"path":"api/tags/环境安装.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%BC%95%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.引言</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.环境安装</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-1-jdk%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.1 jdk安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a clas